\id 2TI - Mwela Bible Version
\h 2 TIMOTEO
\toc1 Bhaluwa ja Bhili ja a Pauli kwa a Timoteo
\toc2 2 Timoteo
\toc3 2 TMT
\mt2 Bhaluwa ja Bhili ja a Pauli kwa a
\mt1 Timoteo
\imt1 Shilongolelo
\ip Shitabhu sha 2 kwa a Timoteo ni bhaluwa ja bhili ja a Ntume a Pauli ku bhaajiganywa bhabho a Timoteo. Bhaluwa ja bhili ja a Timoteo pujajandikwe na a Pauli mobha ga tome na kuwa kwabho. Gene mobhago pubhaliji bhali bhatabhilwe ku Loma (1:16). A pauli pubhaliji na shilongani sha punda na a Timoteo na kaje pubhaashemaga bhana bhabho (Bhapilipi 2:22, 1:2, 1:18).
\ip Jejino ni bhaluwa jimo munkumbi gwa bhaluwa nsheshe ibhajandishe a Pauli kwa mena ga bhandu, kuleka lina lya Likanisha. Itatu ina ya yene bhaluwayo ni, 1 Timoteo na Tito na Pilimoni. Malanga pujajandikwe bhaluwa ja bhili kwa a Timoteo, Bhakilishitu bha muutawala gwa Loma bhatendaga potekwanga. Genego ni gapeleshele a Pauli bhatabhwe, na a Timoteo bhatendaga kwiipililila na gwene ukomugo. Malinga mmaluwa ja ntai ja kwa a Timoteo, a Pauli bhanakwaaleya a Timoteo ga bhaajiganya bha unami (1 Timoteo 1:16-18). Na kabhili a Pauli bhanakwaalugulila a Timoteo kuti ganakwiya mobha ga shilaje (3:1).
\iot Ipali Mwenemo
\io1 1. A Pauli bhanaatandubha kwa kwaalamushila a Timoteo (1:1-2) na kabhili bhanakwaataga ntima (1:3-18).
\io1 2. Kabhili a Pauli bhanakwaakwiya a Timoteo ga kwiipililila (2:1-13).
\io1 3. A Pauli bhanakwaapa a Timoteo malajilo gana ga pamo (2:14-26). 4, Kungai a Pauli bhanakwaaleya a Timoteo ga indu ikwiya na namuna ja mmbone ja tenda.
\io1 4. A Pauli bhanamalishiya kwa matalashiyo gabho bhayene kwa a Timoteo (4:9-24).
\c 1
\s1 Shalamu
\p 
\v 1 Nne a Pauli, kwa pinga kwabho a Nnungu, njemilwe kubha ntume jwa a Yeshu Kilishitu, nkupinga nunguye ga gumi gubhalajile a Nnungu tupegwe, nkulundana na a Yeshu Kilishitu,
\v 2 ngunakunnjandishila mmwe mmanangu a Timoteo bhungumpinga.
\p Ngunakumpinjila mboka, na shiya, na ulele ikoposhela kwa Atati a Nnungu, na a Yeshu Kilishitu Bhakulungwa bhetu.
\s1 Kutenda Eja na Tagwa Ntima
\p 
\v 3 Ngunakwaatendela eja a Nnungu bhungwatendela liengo kwa ntima gwa mmbone malinga shibhatendangaga ashaambuje bhukala, ngunakwaatendela eja kila pungunkumbushila mmwe mobha gowe, nkujuga kwangu shilo na mui.
\v 4 Pungukumbushila minyoi jenu, ngunalokolila kummona nkupinga kuangalala kwangu kupunde.
\v 5 Ngunakumbushila ngulupai jenu ja kweli, ngulupai jatandubhile kwa anakulu bhenu a Loishi na anyinabhenu a Eunike. Kwa nneyo ngunakulupalila kuti, jipali nkali kwenu mmwe.
\v 6 Kwa nneyo ngunakunkumbushiya kuti nkwiye shipaji sha a Nnungu, shimposhele punammishile makono.
\v 7 Pabha a Nnungu bhangatupa Mbumu jwa bhoga, ikabhe Mbumu jwa mashili, na jwa pingana, na jwa kwiitimalika.
\p 
\v 8 Bhai nnakole oni kong'ondela ga Bhakulungwa bhetu, nkali kungolela oni nne ndabhilwe kwa ligongo lyabho. Ikabheje mme pamo na nne mmboteko kwa ligongo lya Ngani ja Mmbone, malinga shinkupegwa mashili na a Nnungu.
\v 9 Bhene bhatutapwile nikutushema tubhe tubhandu bhabho bha ukonjelo, nngabha kwa ligongo lya itendi yetu, ikabhe kwa ligongo lya pinga kwabho na nema jabho bhayene. Jene nemaji twashinkupegwa nkulundana na a Yeshu Kilishitu kuumila bhukalago.
\v 10 Kwa nneyo, jene nemaji nnaino jishiibhulwa bhakayuyweje bhaatapula bhetu a Yeshu Kilishitu. Bhenebho bhashikugapeya mashili ga shiwo, nipeleshela gumi gwa pitipiti kwa Ngani ja Mmbone.
\p 
\v 11 Kwa ligongo lya jene Ngani ja Mmboneji, nne njiagulwa kubha nkulunguya, na ntume na nkujiganya.
\v 12 Kwa ligongo lya genego, nne ngunapotekwa, nkali nneyo ngakola oni, pabha naamanyi bhene bhungwaakulupalila bhala, numbe nimumanyi kuti shibhashibhishile ulinda shene shibhambele shila, mpaka kuishila lyubha lya mpelo.
\v 13 Nkamulile ukoto majiganyo ga kweli guninnjigenye gala, na ngulupai na nkupingana kwa nkulundana na a Yeshu Kilishitu.
\v 14 Kwa Mbumu jwa Ukonjelo atama nkati jetu, nshibhishile ulinda shene shindu sha mmbone shimpegwilwe shila.
\p 
\v 15 Malinga shimmumanyi kuti bhandu bhowe bha ku Ashia, bhaneshilenje, munkumbi gwabhonji bhaapali a Pigelo na a Elimogene.
\v 16 Bhakulungwa bhaabhonelanje shiya bha ulongo bha a Oneshipolashi, pabha bhatendaga ndaga ntima wala bhakakolaga oni ga tabhwa kwangu.
\v 17 Ikabhe bhakaisheje ku Loma, gubhatumbile kunoleya, mpaka gubhamweni.
\v 18 Bhakulungwa a Yeshu bhaabhonele shiya sha a Nnungu lyene lyubhalyo! Na mmwe mmumanyi indu yaigwinji ibhandendele ku Epesho kula.
\c 2
\s1 Linjola jwa Mmbone jwa a Yeshu Kilishitu
\p 
\v 1 Bhai ugwe mwanangu, ukole mashili kwa nema jitupegwa nkulundana na a Yeshu Kilishitu.
\v 2 Na majiganyo gumpilikene ngulijiganya pa bhaakong'ondela bhabhagwinji, numbe mmwe mwaajiganyanje bhandunji bhaakulupalika, bhaakombolanga kwaajiganyanga bhananji.
\p 
\v 3 Gwiilunde mmboteko pamo na nne, malinga nkomana ngondo jwa mmbone jwa a Yeshu Kilishitu.
\v 4 Linjola pabha nkukomana ngondo akakwiibhuka nkukamula maengo gana, pabha shaapinga ni kwaanonyeya bhakulungwa bha likundi lyakwe.
\v 5 Nneyo peyo mundu apwatanila upo mwiing'ando, akapegwa upo ya kombola monaga jwangakaguya ikubho ya nng'andogo.
\v 6 Mundu atumbila kulima, ni apinjikwa abhe jwantai kupata shipeta sha mauno.
\v 7 Nnganishiye kaje malobhe gungummalanjila gano, pabha Bhakulungwa shibhampe lumanyio lwa kugamanya gowe.
\p 
\v 8 Mwaakumbushile a Yeshu Kilishitu bhayushiywe bhakaweje, bha shipinga sha a Daudi, malinga shijitaya Ngani ja Mmbone jingulunguya jino.
\v 9 Kwa lyene ligongolyo ngunapotekwa nitabhwa mbuti nkulebha, ikabheje lilobhe lya a Nnungu likatabhwa.
\v 10 Kwa nneyo ngunakwiipililila gowe, kwa ligongo lya bhandunji bhaagwilwenje na a Nnungu, nkupinga na bhalabhonji bhapatanje ntapulo nkulundana na a Yeshu Kilishitu, na ukonjelo gwa pitipiti.
\v 11 Na malobhe ga kulupalika gakuti,
\q1 “Monaga tuwile pamo na bhenebho,
\q1 nneyo peyo shitulame pamo na bhenebho.
\q1 
\v 12 Monaga shituipililile,
\q1 shitutagwale pamo na bhenebho.
\q1 Na ibhaga shitwaakane bhenebho,
\q1 na bhalabho shibhatukane uwe.
\q1 
\v 13 Nkali tubhe bhangakulupalilanga,
\q1 bhenebho ni bhaakulupalikape,
\q1 pabha ikaakomboleka kwiikana bhayene.”
\s1 Nkamula Maengo Apingwa na a Nnungu
\p 
\v 14 Bhai, mwaakumbushiyanje bhandu gene malobhego, na mwaaleyanje pa meyo ga a Nnungu, bhanakolanje malobhe ga mitau, pabha gangali mana, ikabhe ganapuganya bhaapilikananga.
\v 15 Ntumbile kwiilanguya kwa a Nnungu kuti mmaakulupalika, ntumishi jwangali oni, nnilunguya kwa aki ntenga gwa kweli gwa a Nnungu.
\v 16 Mwiembuye na nkungulu gwangali mana na gwa shingumba, pabha ganakwaashoyanga bhandunji nngulupai niileka kwaajogopa a Nnungu.
\v 17 Majiganyo gabhonji ganajambushiya malinga libhanga shilijenela nshiilu, munkumbi gwabhonji bhapalinji a Imenayo na a Piletushi.
\v 18 Bhanganyabho bhapuganikenje niileka ya kweli, bhalinkutinji kuyuywa kwa bhandunji kupitile, nipuganya ngulupai ya bhandu bhabhagwinji.
\v 19 Ikabheje a Nnungu bhabhishile ishi ya nyumba, ishimilishwe kwa olela ukoto, na gene malobhe gano, gashijandikwa pantundu yene ishii, “Bhakulungwa bhaamanyi bhandunji bhabho,” na kabhili, “Kila ashema lina lya Bhakulungwa, aleshe ilebho.”
\p 
\v 20 Nnyumba jikulungwa ikaapagwa indu ya shaabhu na ela pe, ikabhe na indu ya mikongo na ya lilongo, ina ya tendela maengo gamashoko ina ya maengo gamakulungwa.
\v 21 Bhai mundu aikonjeleyaga niileka ilebho, shaabhe mundu jwa maengo gamakulungwa, sha ukonjelo shibhishilwe na bhayene nyumba, shaapwae kwa kila liengo lya mmbone.
\p 
\v 22 Mwiembuye na ilokoli ya ushanda, nkagulile uguja na ngulupai na kupingana na ulele, pamo na bhene bhakwaajuganga Bhakulungwa kwa ntima gwa mmbone.
\v 23 Mwiembuye na mitau ja shingumba na jangali mana, pabha mmumanyi kuti yeneyo inakumbuya mipwai.
\v 24 Numbe ntumishi jwa Bhakulungwa akapinjikwa kubha jwa mipwai, ikabhe jwa kwiitimalika kubhandu bhowe, akombola kujiganya na kwiipililila.
\v 25 Anapinjikwa kwaaleyanga kwa kwiitimalika bhakuntaukanga, pana a Nnungu shibhaajalianje kwiipeta nikagula ya kweli.
\v 26 Nkupinga lunda lwabhonji lwaabhujilanje kabhili nikolobhoka nniyau lika Lishetani, lyabhatanjiyenje nkupinga bhatendanje yapinga jwenejo.
\c 3
\s1 Atali ya Mobha ga Kumpelo
\p 
\v 1 Ikabheje nnapinjikwa mmumanye kuti mobha ga kumpelo shigabhe ga atali.
\v 2 Pabha, bhandunji shibhabhanganje bhakwiipinganga ashayenenji, na bhapinganga mmbiya, na bhakwiiniyanga, na bha mbwinya, na bhaatukananga, na bhakakwaakundanga bhaakwetenje, na bhakaapinganga kutenda eja, na bhangalinginji bha mmbone.
\v 3 Shibhakoposhelanje bhandunji bhakakwaapinganga ashaalongo ajabhonji, na bhakaapinganga kumaliya mipwai, na bhalambililanga, na bhakakwiitimalikanga, na bha kolanga nngomo, na bhakaapinganga kutenda ya mmbone,
\v 4 bhaatendebhukana, na bhamitau, na bhakwiipunanga, na bhapinganga ya manong'a, kupunda kwaapinga a Nnungu.
\v 5 Bhalinginji mbuti bhakwaatindibhalilanga a Nnungu, ikabheje bhalikananga mashili ga a Nnungu, mwiembuye na bhene bhanganyabho.
\p 
\v 6 Pabha munkumbi gwabhonji bhapalinji bhaowelanga mmajumba ga bhandu, nikwaatekeyanga bhanabhakongwe bhangalinginji lunda, bhakwetenje mishigo ja ilebho na ilokoli yaigwinji,
\v 7 bhene bhanabhakongwebho bhalikwiijiganyanga mobha gowe, ikabheje bhakakolanga lunda lwa kuimanya indu ya kweli.
\v 8 Ni malinga a Yaneshi na a Yambuleshi bhaataukenje a Musha, nneyo peyo na bhene bhaataukanga indu ya mmbone, bhandu bhaangabhanikenje lunda lwabhonji, bhakanilwenje nngulupai.
\v 9 Ikabheje bhakapundanga kutenda nneyo, pabha ubhelu gwabhonji shigumanyishe na bhandu bhowe, malinga puyaliji kwa a Yane na a Yambule.
\s1 Malajilo ga Kumpelo
\p 
\v 10 Ikabheje mmwe nkagwile majiganyo na ndamo jangu, na ng'aniyo na ngulupai yangu, na kwiitimalika kwangu, na kupingana na kwiipililila kwangu,
\v 11 ga mboteko na laga. Yani ku Antiokia, na ku Ikonio, na ku Lishitila, na gowe ga jogoya gunaipililile! Ikabheje Bhakulungwa gubhandapwile mowemo.
\v 12 Bhai, bhowe bhaapinganga kutama nkwaakulupalila a Kilishitu Yeshu, shibhapotekwanje.
\v 13 Bhandu bha ilebho, na bha unami shibhapundanje kutenda ilebho, bhalitembanga na tembwanga.
\v 14 Ikabheje, mmwe ntame mmajiganyo gunnjigenywe nikugaposhela ukoto gala, pabha mwaamanyinji bhannjigenyenje bhala.
\v 15 Numbe kuumila pumwaliji mmashoko mwagamanyi Majandiko ga Ukonjelo, ga kumpa ng'aniyo ya lunda ya kuntapula kwa ngulupai ya nkulundana na a Yeshu Kilishitu.
\v 16 Majandiko gowe gajandikwe nkulongoywa na Mbumu jwa a Nnungu, ganapwaa nkujiganya na nkuleya bhandu muilebho yabhonji, na kwaalongoyanga, nikwaapanganga aki,
\v 17 nkupinga mundu jwa a Nnungu atimilile, na aengwe kutenda maengo gowe ga mmbone.
\c 4
\s1 Malajilo ga Kumpelo
\p 
\v 1 Ngunakunnajila pa meyo ga a Nnungu na a Yeshu Kilishitu, bhaapinga kwaukumulanga bhandunji bhabhakoto na bhawilenje, pene pushibhaishe mu upalume gwabho.
\v 2 Nnunguye lyene lilobheli, na nnjime ukoto mobha gowe, gapwaa na ganngapwaa, na nkalipile, na nnimbiye, na mwaaleyanje bhandu nnikwaajiganyanga kwiitimalika.
\v 3 Pabha shigaishe mobha gushibhakananje majiganyo ga kweli ga gumi, ikabheje shibhakagulilanje ng'aniyo yabhonji, nikwiigumbashiya bhaajiganya bhabhonji bhabhagwinji, nkupinga bhapilikananje indu ikwaanonyelanga.
\v 4 Numbe shibhakananje kupilikanishiya malobhe ga kweli, nitendebhushila ndango ya unami.
\v 5 Ikabheje mmwe ntame nkwiitimalika na indu yowe, mwiipililile mmboteko, nkamule liengo lya lunguya Ngani ja Mmbone, mmalishiye liengo lyenu.
\p 
\v 6 Pabha, nnaino nne ngunashoywa mbuti mbepei, malanga gangu gawa gaishile.
\v 7 Njikomana ngondo ja mmbone ja ngulupai, mwanja nigumaliye, na njikamulila ukoto ngulupai.
\v 8 Nnaino, njibhishilwa shilemba sha aki shishibhambe Bhakulungwa lyene lyubhalyo, numbe ngabha nne pe nne, ikabheje na bhandu bhowe nkwaapinga bhanalolelanga kuika kwabho.
\s1 Malajilo
\p 
\v 9 Ntende shangu kwiya akuno.
\v 10 Pabha a Dema ga pinga indu ya pa shilambolyo, bhashineka gubhapite ku Teshalonike, na a Keleshike gubhapite ku Galatia, na a Tito bhapite ku Dalimatia.
\v 11 Bhali na nne apano, ni a Luka jikape. Mwaaloleye a Maliko, nnjiye nabho, pabha bhananyanguta mmaengo.
\v 12 A Tikiko naatumile ku Epesho.
\v 13 Pushinnjiyepo nnyigalile likoti lyangu lineshile kwa a Kalipashi bha ku Toloa, nnyigalile na itabhu, na kaje ya mapende ila.
\p 
\v 14 A Alekishanda bha yana itale bhala, bhashindendela ya nyata yaigwinji, Bhakulungwa shibhaalipe kwa itendi yabho.
\v 15 Na mmwe mwiiteije na bhenebho, pabha bhashinkutauka kwa puya malobhe getu.
\p 
\v 16 Punaibheleketelaga malobhe ga kwiitapula gwa ntai, jwakwa mundu ajimi na nne kunyangutila, ikabhe bhowe bhashinkunekanga, nne ngunakwaajujilanga kwa a Nnungu bhaleshelelwanje, na bhanabhonekanje kulebha kwa genego!
\v 17 Ikabheje Bhakulungwa gubhajimi na nne, nigubhambele mashili, nkupinga nunguye ntenga gula ukoto, nkali ku bhandu bha ilambo ina, na nne gundapwilwe nshiwo, mbuti ngutapulwa nkang'wa ja imba.
\v 18 Bhakulungwa shibhandapule na indu yowe ya nyata, shibhandole ng'ishe ku Upalume gwabho gwa ku nnungu. Ukonjelo ni gwabho pitipiti! Amina.
\s1 Shalamu sha Kumpelo
\p 
\v 19 Mwaalamushilanje a Pilishika na a Akula na bhandunji bha munngwabho a Oneshipolashi.
\v 20 A Elashito kubhatama ku Kolinto, na a Tolopimo kunaaleshile ku Mileto, bhalwele.
\p 
\v 21 Ntende shangu kwiya akuno, gakanabhe ishila mobha ga mmbepo. A Ebhulo bhanakunnamushilanga, na a Pudenishi na a Linushi, na a Kilaudia, na Bhakilishitu bhowe.
\p 
\v 22 Bhakulungwa bhatame muntima gwenu. Nema jitame na mmanganyanji mmowe.
